# Sprint 23 (ADR-077) — per-run eval outputs (transcripts, scores, manifests,
# per-run REPORT.md). The curated closing report at
# evals/lavern-jv/reports/sprint-23-baseline.md is checked in; everything in
# runs/<ts>/ is per-execution and not committed.
evals/lavern-jv/runs/*
!evals/lavern-jv/runs/.gitkeep
